---
title: Quick Bacon, Cherry Tomato & Pesto Fusilli with Parmesan & Pear Salad
description: Presenting a few of our favourite things: cherry tomatoes, bacon, Parmesan cheese and basil pesto. All of those deep flavours
meld together wonderfully when tossed through spirals of fusilli. Along with a crunchy pear salad, this'll be bumped up to a
champion household dinner in no time!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-bacon-cherry-tomato-pesto-fusilli-d8b7c116.jpg
